data.description:
Inviting 3 bed 2 bath home located in the Autumn Ridge subdivision. This home welcomes you with tall ceilings, open floor concept, and a bright and spacious kitchen. Enjoy the Oklahoma evenings on the back patio with a large backyard space and plenty of room for your pets, kids, or gardening. This home boasts large rooms, plenty of closet space, and a spacious mudroom. Don't miss out on this home- come check it out!
